{"tid":686942,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"非常嚴重便秘覺得自己d屎就黎爆炸","createTime":"2018-06-01T18:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T09:17:57.000Z","uid":82278,"like":143,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"b6302bb99e7dfd3ef110d1ed4e0abe59e839baae","tid":686942,"uid":82278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:07:46.000Z","msg":"好似差唔多一個星期冇痾到屎<br />\n其實唔肚痛 望落個肚都唔係好凸 但係就覺得好漲 個人冇乜胃口 好似頂住頂住咁<br />\nkeep住個屎眼都有便意 但係去到廁所又痾唔到<br />\n一係就feel到舊屎kick住係屎眼 縮到出唔到<br />\n<br />\n去診所睇醫生 佢淨係開瀉藥俾我 食完都冇feel<br />\n<br />\n應唔應該去醫院灌腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係自己買兩個甘油條塞 但係自己真係唔知點塞落屎眼...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba9541e4f6c9ac250ca8d1867cd5a5072abea25","tid":686942,"uid":31371,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:09:06.000Z","msg":"有冇用過咩便利通果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60d5be6ab901b4abb6e3ed7be62b3062bf4352b","tid":686942,"uid":171958,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:10:32.000Z","msg":"食多d西瓜<br />\n利：一日去兩次，食完西瓜去3次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ee5c560f4490589e512bcb99a453d2a7a41c56","tid":686942,"uid":4874,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:11:22.000Z","msg":"用條J通通佢"},{"pid":"9201db5e889737fd721d4aa259e5f1ac7d34d591","tid":686942,"uid":68746,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:12:29.000Z","msg":"有無飲西梅汁"},{"pid":"0813c033a4c08123a4c64179d91a2883